  max_counted: 1
  min_needed: 1
  explanation: |-
    <i>Editor's Note: Students do not enroll in any numbered course for this requirement, so hoagieplan does not check it.</i><br><br>
    Students undertake independent research, which may take one of three forms
    1) a senior thesis with a substantial archaeological component; <br>
    2) a junior paper on an archaeological topic; <br>
    3) or a 25-page research paper on an archaeological topic. <br><br>

    Independent work must be submitted by 5:00pm on Dean's Date. Only theses
    are eligible for the Frederick Barnard White Prize in Archaeology.
