      (LIN 301, LIN 302, LIN 303, LIN 306; LIN 303 may be substituted 
      with PHI/LIN 334)
    pdfs_allowed: 1
    course_list:
    - LIN 301
    - LIN 302
    - LIN 303
    - LIN 306
    - PHI 334 / LIN 334
  - name: Methods Courses
    max_counted: 1
    min_needed: 1
    explanation: At least one course from the set of "methods" courses 
      (LIN 210, LIN 310, LIN 355, LIN 356.
    pdfs_allowed: 1
    course_list:
    - LIN 210
    - LIN 310
    - LIN 355
    - LIN 356
  - name: Elective Courses
    max_counted: 1
    min_needed: 2
